      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAWRENNY BOYS (2) has been narrowly beaten his last two and has the top hoop aboard today. Races forward and is well placed to break through. LIGHT FORCE (1) hit the frame when resuming at this track but couldn't back it up last start over 1200m at Launceston. Presents fitter with some gear tweaks and can improve into the finish. DINA TYCOON (5) was in the firing line all the way placing on the synthetic first-up. The former Victorian will be better for that and would be right in the finish at best. UNA PALOMA BLANCA (7) hasn't been far away and has a low gate today and a handy 2kg claim. In the mix. BLACK RAPTOR (4) has the rail and did enough here two back on debut to consider.",
